descriptionHtml:
Large city for construction with [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/22330/]Tundra Defense[/url]. Has a navmeshes! Entrance on roof of Whiterun barracks.

[u]Locations:[/u]
The city center with lights 3 * 3 cell
Stable
Garden
Cemetery
Temple
Park with statues
Government district
Shooting range
Park with ponds
Tropical oasis
Zoo
Also contains a house without furniture, for your personal creativity.

[b]setting[/b]
Put it in the data folder, but it is better to use a specialized installer.
[b]removal[/b]
Delete files and folders whose names have «FineWinds».

changelog:
[b]v.0.1[/b] City only.
[b]v.0.1a[/b] Begun construction of the island, added national symbols and 2 shields, one of them crafting. The city was named Heldgard! Now there's a teleport from "North maden". Beautify the city. Outlined the main location, the roads, while running on the road "Coast" (dark orange) - 4 minutes. Do not ask me where that is, it is always better to explore everything!
